name: Vanderpump Dogs
overview: Fans and pet lovers go deeper into Lisa Vanderpump's luxurious life in this series chronicling the stories and adoptions that occur at her beloved namesake foundation: Vanderpump Dogs.
tagline: Getting a new leash on life.

episodes.name: A Paw-fect Proposal
episodes.overview: Introducing the Vanderpump Dogs rescue center. Lisa searches for the right dog for a couple whose special day hinges on finding the perfect fit for their family. A client seeks a very specific kind of companion for her pampered pup.

episodes.name: The Doggy Wears Prada
episodes.overview: A client seeks the perfect service dog to help her gain independence. A fashion-forward potential owner wants a glamorous pup to bring onto the red carpet.

episodes.name: Twinsies
episodes.overview: Twins hope to assert their independence by adopting their own pooches. A six-year-old girl tries to prove to Lisa that she is responsible enough to adopt a dog; a previous adoption takes an unexpected twist.

episodes.name: 10 Is the New 5
episodes.overview: A law student sets her sights on rescuing a tripod. Lisa and her staff pull out all the stops to find the perfect dog for an indecisive client.

episodes.name: The Princess and the Pup
episodes.overview: A family of three seeks a cuddly, hypoallergenic dog. Lisa struggles to help a couple with an unsocialized dog.
